title: Monthly Chapter Meeting - Guest Speaker: Eric Dienst – Reno Air Racer
location: EAA Chapter 22 - Cottonwood Airport, 5105 Auburn St, Rockford, IL 61101, USA
description:
Guest Speaker: Eric Dienst – Reno Air Racer

Eric Dienst, Reno Air Race competitor, will share stories and insights from racing at Reno. Learn what it takes to prepare, compete, and fly at race speeds in one of aviation’s most iconic events. This promises to be a fascinating and high-energy presentation.

Join with Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/iri-wdsd-rie
Or dial: (US) +1 929-220-3848 PIN: 133769963#
More phone numbers: https://tel.meet/iri-wdsd-rie?pin=2300650633625&hs=7

Learn more about Meet at: https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720

title: VMC/IMC Club
location: EAA Chapter 22 - Cottonwood Airport, 5105 Auburn St, Rockford, IL 61101, USA
description:
Join us for our monthly EAA VMC/IMC Club session — an interactive hangar-style discussion focused on real-world flying decisions. Using FAA safety scenarios and guided discussion, we’ll work through weather analysis, risk management, aeronautical decision making, and “what would you do?” moments in both VFR and IFR operations.

Open to all pilots and aviation enthusiasts. Come share experiences, sharpen your skills, and learn from each other in a relaxed, no-pressure environment focused on safer flying.
